<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_A.baseDesc>他曾經是一名獲得勳章的 NCR 上校，如今卻以冷酷無情的效率帶領著逃兵，在荒地上開疆拓土。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_A.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_A.title>流氓上校</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_A.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_A.titleShort>上校</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_A.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_B.baseDesc>這位上校以其戰場戰術而聞名，因不服從命令而被流放，現在指揮著一支流氓軍隊。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_B.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_B.title>流亡戰術家</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_B.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_B.titleShort>戰術家</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_B.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_C.baseDesc>懷著建立新秩序的願景，這位上校拋棄了 NCR，成為廢土流放者中令人畏懼的軍閥。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_C.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_C.title>廢土軍閥</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_C.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_C.titleShort>軍閥</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_C.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_D.baseDesc>這位曾經受人尊敬的上校後來失寵，導致他聚集逃兵，在荒原上開闢了一條新道路。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_D.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_D.title>丟臉的領袖</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_D.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_D.titleShort>領導者</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_D.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_E.baseDesc>這位經驗豐富、雄心勃勃的上校拋棄了指揮僱傭兵的方式，並開創了自己的事業。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_E.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_E.title>僱傭兵指揮官</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_E.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_E.titleShort>指揮官</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Colonel_E.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_A.baseDesc>他曾經是一名 NCR 警官，利用自己的軍銜謀取私利，直到他的罪行被發現。現在他在荒原上帶領逃兵。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_A.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_A.title>腐敗中尉</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_A.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_A.titleShort>中尉</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_A.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_B.baseDesc>由於對 NCR 的領導不力感到沮喪，這名軍官選擇開小差，將自己的戰術技能更好地運用到流氓隊伍中。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_B.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_B.title>幻滅的戰略家</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_B.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_B.titleShort>戰略家</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_B.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_C.baseDesc>這位指揮官因質疑命令而被驅逐，現在帶領逃兵與前盟友和敵人作戰。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_C.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_C.title>流亡指揮官</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_C.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_C.titleShort>指揮官</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_C.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_D.baseDesc>這位擅長談判的軍官為了新派系的生存而放棄了斡旋交易和聯盟。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_D.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_D.title>荒地外交官</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_D.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_D.titleShort>外交官</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_D.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_E.baseDesc>在向 NCR 復仇的驅使下，這位隊長開小差，領導攻擊他以前的戰友並伸張正義。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_E.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_E.title>復仇隊長</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_E.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_E.titleShort>隊長</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Officer_E.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_A.baseDesc>他曾經是一名忠誠的 NCR 士兵，但對無休止的競選活動和腐敗的軍官感到厭倦。現在，他與逃兵同伴一起為生存而戰。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_A.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_A.title>幻滅的步槍手</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_A.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_A.titleShort>步槍手</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_A.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_B.baseDesc>這位士兵在戰鬥中受傷並被指揮部遺棄，為了逃離一個不再關心自己的系統而逃亡。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_B.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_B.title>受傷的退伍軍人</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_B.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_B.titleShort>老將</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_B.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_C.baseDesc>這位偵察兵擅長在荒地中航行，他離開了 NCR，利用自己的才能謀求自己的生存和利益。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_C.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_C.title>清道夫偵察兵</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_C.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_C.titleShort>偵察</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_C.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_D.baseDesc>懷抱著致富夢想，這位士兵放棄了 NCR，成為一名僱傭槍手，將自己的技能賣給出價最高的人。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_D.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_D.title>僱傭兵候選者</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_D.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_D.titleShort>有志者</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_D.titleShort>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_E.baseDesc>一旦擔負保護 NCR 資產的任務，一個錯誤就會導致恥辱和開小差。現在他在被遺棄的人中尋求救贖。</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_E.baseDesc>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_E.title>恥辱的守衛</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_E.title>
  <FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_E.titleShort>警衛</FCP_Backstory_NCR_Deserter_Trooper_E.titleShort>
</LanguageData>
